name: Vessels 186: The Blue Devil
description:
The upper classes of the colony brought all manner of technologies with them when they abandoned most of the Earth’s population to a dark fate.  Their longevity and appearance can be altered in drastic ways.  

This particular chap knows he is a bad man and aped in hard to his performative personality- actually having devils horns grafted onto his skull and his eyes modified to have that strange blue sheen.  

He is far older than he appears and has many years in which to do many terrible things to many innocent people.  He has yet to face any consequences for his actions..
